/ Smoke test of Cut 4 at the goal layer. The hard probe (body's _value
/ stays null after the property read) lives in C# HttpChannelTests; this
/ goal test pins the surface: %response!status% reads metadata, the
/ subsequent %response.field% reads the body. Result of the body read
/ depends on the live endpoint; the smoke is that both calls succeed and
/ http.response no longer exists as a parallel type.
- get http https://httpbin.org/json
    write to %response%
- assert %response!status% equals 200
- assert %response.slideshow.author% equals "Yours Truly"
